@StepCounter_HostAddress = http://localhost:5156

### Get all teams
GET {{StepCounter_HostAddress}}/api/teams
Accept: application/json

### Create a team
POST {{StepCounter_HostAddress}}/api/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Marketing Ninjas"
}

### Get team step count
GET {{StepCounter_HostAddress}}/api/teams/{teamId}/steps
Accept: application/json